! 🌐 UPlanet

is a ''decentralized, non-commercial, and resilient free information system''.

UPlanet is a decentralized social network that aims to revolutionize how we manage and share information, with a unique grid system dividing the globe into sectors, each representing localized data. It empowers users by allowing them to register their own TiddlyWiki in their area, maintaining control over their data, and resolving conflicts through a signature-based system. 

The network integrates with Astroport, an IPFS distributed storage software, enhancing data security and accessibility, and operates on core principles of decentralization, data refinement through a web of trust, and user-centric navigation.

